item.title: Coney Island
item.description: This trip to coney island, doesn’t feel real. Feels like a dream, or a poorly made computer game. You can only observe, cannot interact. Everything happenning here, has nothing to do with me. Not even a penny. Even a penny, has its own purpose. It circulate in the global economy. Whereas me, alone. Always expecting some chemical reactions. But there is only locked up tensions inside my head. Thought it’s finally the time to get relaxed.
